descriptionHTML:
Inspiration Watch Face Design Atelier presents " BOXER "

Boxer is a beautiful watch face with black diamond metal dial
and brushed platinium hands. Futuristic design with classical lines. Enhance your Smartwatch
with a high class look and discover the maximum.

It works on all Android Wear devices and supports round and square smartwatches.
Round ( Moto 360 and LG G watch R )
Square ( LG G watch and Samsung Gear Live, ASUS Zen Watch and Sony Smartwatch 3 )

Boxer analog watchface adds a powerfull look to your android wear.

Key Custom features

★ powerfull design
★ clear readability
★ battery saving ambient mode design
★ watch battery widget indicator
★ watch date of month widget indicator
★ watch widgets indicators optional on / off
★ supports round and squared watches
★ smooth seconds move


Customization of Boxer watch face

✔ Open Android Wear app
✔ Select Boxer watch face in the selection
✔ One Click on the icon activates the watch face on your smart watch device
✔ Then Double click on icon brings you to customization page
✔ Now you can customize Boxer watch face ( date widget on /off and battery watch widget on / off )

( important: You may have to wait a minute to transfer to your watch over Bluetooth )

Inspiration Germany Smart Watch & Android wearable design Atelier ©
